The paper discusses the use of standard state-space models in representing different notions of awareness, which is a topic closely related to game theory (cs.GT) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions completeness and decidability results, which are topics in logic (cs.LO) and mathematical analysis (cs.MA). Finally, the paper discusses the use of propositional quantifiers, which is a topic in discrete mathematics (cs.DS).
